{
  "name": "Apothic Dismembered Greed*",
  "type": "equipment",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A dismembered kobold hand that has turned grayish in color hanging from a leather cord to be worn like a necklace.</p><p>When the wearer of this necklace is within 10ft of a secret or hidden pathway, passage, door, trap, pattern, codes, symbols, or objects (DM's discretion); the claw will itch and scratch the attuned user and point in the direction of the secret or hidden element.</p><p>While attuned you are able to cast <strong>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.spells.Item.1mSmSMfpGVk5QyAT]{Mage Hand}</strong><em><strong> </strong></em>that appears as a spectral gray kobold's claw. You can also use the claw as a familiar as per the <strong>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.spells.Item.g1LnuxtrOGoXC2IN]{Find Familiar (Apothic Dismembered Greed)}</strong> spell, with no material components required.</p><p><strong>Fidgeting Claw.</strong><em><strong> </strong></em>While attuned to this necklace and the <strong>Crawling Claw</strong> is affixed to the cord your hands become quick and nimble, allowing them to get into places they shouldn't or to perform movements of fine motor skills. Your are able to use the claw as both tinker's tools and thieves' tools, and you are considered proficient in both.</p><p>While the <strong>Crawling Claw</strong> is in its active state or regenerating the wearer does not have access to <strong>Fidgeting Claw</strong> or the <strong>Mage Hand</strong> spell.</p><p>While attuned, you are able to cast the <strong>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.spells.Item.yGFGZKjd1xX6OrVD]{Find Traps}</strong> spell<span style=\"color:#000000\">, but only once per day and only when the <strong>Crawling Claw</strong> is attached to the cord.</span></p><blockquote><p><strong>When you receive/attune to this item, you will need to manually add the @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.spells.Item.1mSmSMfpGVk5QyAT]{Mage Hand}, @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.spells.Item.yGFGZKjd1xX6OrVD]{Find Traps}, and @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.spells.Item.g1LnuxtrOGoXC2IN]{Find Familiar (Apothic Dismembered Greed)} spells to your character sheet.</strong></p></blockquote>",
      "chat": ""
    },
